To add/remove an X.509 identity:

chmod <target-path> ( <[<+|->r][<+|->w][<+|->x]> | <octal-mode> ) (--pattern="X") <cert-file-path>

To add/remove a Identity Provider identity:

chmod <target-path> ( <[<+|->r][<+|->w][<+|->x]> | <octal-mode> ) <identity-provider-path>

To add/remove a username/password token identity:

chmod <target-path> ( <[<+|->r][<+|->w][<+|->x]> | <octal-mode> ) --username=<username> --password=<password> 

or

chmod <target-path> ( <[<+|->r][<+|->w][<+|->x]> | <octal-mode> ) --username=<username> --hashedpass=<passwordhash> 

To add/remove the catch-all "everyone"/"world" identity:

chmod <target-path> ( <[<+|->r][<+|->w][<+|->x]> | <octal-mode> ) --everyone
